Normal
When exactly 1 "Ghostrick" monster you control (and no other cards) is destroyed by battle or by an opponent's card effect and sent to the Graveyard: Target 2 "Ghostrick" monsters in your Graveyard with a different name than the destroyed monster; Special Summon them in face-down Defense Position.
